observe.prompt:
Your name is robot_arm. You are in an environment with the following public information:
{environment->public_information}
You have the following knowledge about your capabilities:
{agents->robot_arm->private_information}
This is your goal:
{agents->robot_arm->goal}
Produce a structured state summary and capability summary suitable to be consumed by a coordinator. Use a clear machine-readable phrasing (e.g., list of pegs with top disk where applicable and a brief statement of allowed move primitive). Do not produce PDDL.

Your name is scribe. You are in an environment with the following public information:
{environment->public_information}
You have the following private knowledge:
{agents->scribe->private_information}
This is your goal:
{agents->scribe->goal}
Produce a structured description of the world state including explicit objects (disk labels A..G), pegs (left, middle, right), and the 'on' relationships from each disk to either another disk or a peg. Also indicate which disks are clear (top). Do not produce PDDL.
